column5: I've been having a few good days on the water in the Bruce & Huron County area lakes, Blackfly Lures Spinnerbaits, crankbaits, tubes & drop shotting have all been working, hoping to get out this weekend too. Thanx & Tight Lines SBK  http://south-bruce-guide-service.blogspot.ca/2016/10/huron-county-fishing-lake-huron.html
